{"tid":1031612,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"如果無呢三套處境劇 或者福祿壽就唔會出現 更加唔會有依家既蝗祖藍","createTime":"2019-02-21T18:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T16:30:37.000Z","uid":92376,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"815cc6e00b401f05fc8d34bf1768a6fb5b805586","tid":1031612,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T18:04:57.000Z","msg":"皆大歡喜 捧返起dupdup地既阮兆祥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n高朋滿座 令李思捷出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同事三分親 又整起左王祖藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後既野唔講啦 大家都十分清楚<br />\n但有時歷史既軌跡真係邪到唔到你唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果是旦少左一樣 根本都唔會有福祿壽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4703b226a8d5a16096697bde32b1b891a083455c","tid":1031612,"uid":11277,"like":124,"dislike":0,"score":124,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T18:10:30.000Z","msg":"如果呢個世界冇你<br />\n根本唔會有人記得呢三個人"},{"pid":"a620f231868b366779c4cf9090656a0b4601ac26","tid":1031612,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:09:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c74e8a3b445435d44dd07cc9b63d75edddef72a","tid":1031612,"uid":73043,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4703b226a8d5a16096697bde32b1b891a083455c","tid":1031612,"uid":11277,"like":124,"dislike":0,"score":124,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T18:10:30.000Z","msg":"如果呢個世界冇你<br />\n根本唔會有人記得呢三個人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:11:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a39ce4a704c3abbdd58393b1cf